<F P=102>  LD2002211594 Prague CT 1 Television Network in Czech 1830 
GMT 20 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2002211594 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague CT 1 Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Czech </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] As of today, there are 177 HIV positive people 
registered in the Czech Republic, and 46 of them have full-blown 
AIDS; 28 people died. In the past few months, the number of 
infected women of reproductive age has grown. Experts estimate 
that the real number of HIV positive people in the Czech 
Republic is approximately 2,000 to 3,000. 

