<H3> <TI>   Ruling Party Sends Delegation to Russia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2402103694 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1003 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2402103694 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


