Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Belgrade, 24 Feb -- A delegation of the Socialist 
Party of Serbia [SPS] led by Mihailo Markovic, a member of its 
executive group, began its first ever visit to Russia today, the 
SPS information department has reported. 
  During their stay in Russia the SPS delegation is expected 
to 
meet representatives from all of Russia's major political 
parties, members of the Russian government, and both houses of 
the Russian parliament, the SPS notes in its statement. 

