<F P=102>  AU2502142994 Prague MLADA FRONTA DNES in Czech 21 Feb 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> AU2502142994 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague MLADA FRONTA DNES </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Czech </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Article by "(lek)": "Falbr at the Head of the New Trade </F>
Union"] 
  [Text] Hradec Kralove--Richard Falbr, until now the 
chairman of the Czech-Moravian Service Employees Trade Union, 
has been elected leader of the UNIOS trade union, which was 
established on Friday [18 February] by the merger of trade 
unions representing workers in services, the gas industry, and 
foreign trade. The new union has approximately 80,000 members. 

