<F P=102>  PY2801154694 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network in 
Portuguese 0900 GMT 28 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY2801154694 </F>
<F P=104>  Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network </F>


<TEXT>
