government's economic plan. He said that now part of it is 
missing. 
  The PPR [Progressive Renewal Party]'s blocking of voting on 
the provisional measure increasing the income tax on large 
companies and creating a control tax on the financial system 
somewhat irritated Finance Minister Fernando Enrique Cardoso. 
