<F P=100> Guatemala </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Terrorist Device' Explodes in Capital; No Casualties </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA3101035394 Guatemala City Cadena de Emisoras Unidas in 
Spanish 0328 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA3101035394 </F>
<F P=104>  Guatemala City Cadena de Emisoras Unidas </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Andres De Leon] </F>
  [Text] A few moments ago, a terrorist device exploded on 
12th Avenue and 19th Street in Zone 1. Three firefighting units 
immediately went to the site but only damage is reported. The 
terrorist device did not cause any casualties. It is the first 
to explode during the referendum process, which is about to 
conclude with the announcement of the official results. 

</TEXT>

